hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Hold the line, please how viagra works nitric oxide When is someone going to stop President Obama from taking away our freedoms. He has got to be the only President I have seen since Carter that is so arrogant and refuses to listen to the will of the people. He is like a spoiled rotten child that if he can’t get his way he will not quit until he does. Why is Congress on both sides of the isle not seeing how dangerous he is to America. Google how the health care law is going to affect working Americans with insurance. Look at how many companies have already cut benefits because of the law. He says he’s all about the middle class but his plans hurt the middle class all the way down. How much do we have to take before we all say enough?
